{
  "description": "This quiz assesses knowledge of HTML5 semantic elements beyond basic tags like <div> and <span>, testing the ability to choose appropriate tags for structure and accessibility. It is moderately challenging, using a light‑hearted, encouraging tone that nudges learners to improve their markup skills. The quiz aims to gauge practical understanding and confidence in applying semantic HTML in real projects.",
  "topics": [
    "HTML5 semantic tags",
    "Web accessibility",
    "Document structure",
    "Best practices for markup"
